---
title: Sausage Meatball Sub and Spiced Fries with Caramelised Onion and Coleslaw
description: This Sausage Meatball Sub and Spiced Fries is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
